Trivia[]

Jax, Grandmaster at Arms
  • He shares quotes with:
    • ▶️    "Gotcha!"
  • ▶️   "Who wants a piece of the champ?" and ▶️   "Imagine if I had a real weapon." are both directly quoted from his original voiceover.
  • ▶️   "I'm a Jax of all trades!" is a play on the phrase "jack of all trades."
  • ▶️   "Surprise! I'm back! ...Aw, no one?" references his old quote ▶️   "Surprise! I'm back!"
  • ▶️   "Bravest hero I ever knew was just a kid. Here's to you, champ." is a reference to Jaximus' quote ▶️   ▶️   "Here's to you, kid.", which in turn was made as a tribute to Joe (see below).
Jax (old)
  • In Co-op vs. AI matches, Jax Bot's greeting line; "Who wants a piece of the champ?", and his line upon the players' victory; "Imagine if I had a real weapon!", were directly taken from his taunt and joke lines respectively:
    • ▶️  "Who wants a piece of the champ?"
    • ▶️  "Imagine if I had a real weapon."
Jaximus
  • ▶️   ▶️  "Here's to you, kid." references Joe, an Ewing's sarcoma patient who, thanks to the Make-A-Wish Foundation, was able to visit Riot Games' headquarters.
    • Jaximus was Joe's favorite skin, and after he passed away in 05-Jun-2012, the Grandmaster at Arms says the line in his memory.[1]
      • Coincidentally and as a result, the skin became the first non-Legendary skin to include any special lines.
Mecha Kingdoms Jax
  • ▶️  "Would you look at that? I finally have a real weapon!" and ▶️  "Maybe use a real weapon next time." are a reference to his default voiceline's joke.
  • ▶️  "This is the best thing since boiled eggs." and ▶️  "My hobbies include saving people, defending kingdoms, and eating eggs boiled at optimal temperatures." reference his love for boiled eggs.
    • All three of his joke lines also make this reference:
      • ▶️  "I like my action the way I like my eggs: hard-boiled."
        • This is also possibly a reference to the famous Hong Kong action movie of the same name.
      • ▶️  "Little known fact, peeling eggs takes longer than saving kingdoms."
      • ▶️  "My happy place is peace, quiet, and a boiled egg."
  • ▶️  "Kid, you're a true warrior." refers to Jaximus' aforementioned line.
  • ▶️   "Surprise! I never left!" references Jax's old quote ▶️   "Surprise! I'm back!"
